# Baseline vs Recursive: AIME 2025 Comparison

## Overview
Compared **Baseline (single-shot)** vs **RecursiveThink** on first 5 AIME 2025 problems using Mistral `mistral-large-latest`.

---

## Results Summary

| Approach | Correct | Accuracy | Avg Time/Problem |
|----------|---------|----------|------------------|
| **Baseline (k=1)** | 5/5 | **100%** | ~24s |
| **RecursiveThink** | 3/5 | **60%** | ~50s |

> **Key Finding**: With sufficient token limit (4096), single-shot baseline **outperforms** recursive approach on these 5 problems!

